  "texts": [
    "Note that only codes with connected Tanner graphs can have a toric layout according to this definition.",
    "An example toric layout is depicted in Fig. 1b.",
    "A code QC(A, B) has a toric layout if there exist i, j, g, h ∈ {1, 2, 3} such that 1.",
    "M A A B B, = i j T g h T and 2.",
    "A A B B ℓm ord()ord()= i j T g h T. Proof."
  ],
